Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:29.55,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}我從前便一直關注
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:32.31,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}唯一珍貴的事物  那便是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:37.72,ED-CN,,0,40,0,,{\an9\fad(240,240)\blur3\3c&H44547B&}我與你的幸福吧
